27:15.348 --> 27:20.553
pretty much remain unfunded? And what has the 
organization done since your retirement? Or has

27:23.796 --> 27:25.818
it pretty much ceased to exist? And has any other 
organization picked up the slack where you all

27:25.858 --> 27:29.041
left off? Well, I retired, but that doesn't mean 
