27:34.305 --> 27:39.150
Future Farmers of America, where we developed for 
them several programs. And the major program that

27:39.890 --> 27:45.755
we worked with them on was their community 
development program. They had chapters from all

27:46.736 --> 27:55.363
over the United States compete for community 
development or area development or rural

27:46.736 --> 27:55.363
development, whatever you want to call it. And 
